giu 13, 2015 10:10:51 PM null
INFORMAZIONI: Inefficient mapping: You have declared that field "models.Prodotto.fornitori" is mapped by collection "models.Fornitore.prodotti".  The mapping would be much more efficient if instead you map "models.Prodotto.fornitori" and declare that "models.Fornitore.prodotti" is mapped by it.
